      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/a-glut-of-coal-in-china-is-set-to-push-falling-prices-even-lower</link>
      <description><![CDATA[冬季来临，中国煤炭产量激增，远远超过需求，导致库存增加、价格暴跌，分析师预测价格还会进一步下跌。]]></description>
